RE Straightline Division of US Steel Sorry I meant to set up the company as a Division not a trade name I am going to change the name Any questions pleas call me Albert Escamilla X Original Message From Clark Claudia Sent Wednesday October PM To Jones Tana Cc Ebow Amber Escamilla Albert Subject Straightline Division of US Steel Tana I received a PA for Straightline Division of US Steel and credit approved I ask Global to create an CP ID and the ID reads Straightline a dba of US Steel Corporation Do I have to ask customer to refax PA with GCP name CP ID or is okay to process like Straightline Division of US Steel Let me know Thank you Claudia

RE Jason Kaniss login ID and password forStack Manager Cc Request Complete Jason Kaniss Global ID EPMI Midwest Desk Albert Escamilla Global Counterparty Original Message From Sturm Fletcher J Sent Wednesday October PM To GCPHouston Cc Sever Stephanie Subject Jason Kaniss login ID and password forStack Manager Please set up Jason Kaniss with a stack manager login and password effective ASAP He will be trading US East Power and US Natural Gas All transactions under his login should go into EPMI Mid West risk book Jason works for me on the MidWest desk and is in training to be the new short term SERC trader at the beginning of next year If you have any questions please call me at x Thanks Fletcher Sturm ps Id like him to be able to get started tomorrow Thur morning am if possible
